Package: svamp
Title: Tools for support in outbreak management and suspicion investigation
Version: 0.2
Date: 2015-09-14
Author: Giampaolo Cocca, Thomas Rosendal
Maintainer: Giampaolo Cocca <giampaolo.cocca@sva.se>
Description: svamp is a package that builds on Rmarkdown.
    Providing PPN and buffers size as input information a report with
    relevant information for outbreak management and suspicion investigation
    within the area under investigation.
License: Internal SVA code
Type: Package
